#: ../../C/cuspy.rst:5
msgid "cuspy"
msgstr "cuspy"

#: ../../C/cuspy.rst:7
msgid "/kuhs´pee/, adj\\."
msgstr "/kuhs´pee/, 形容詞"

#: ../../C/cuspy.rst:9
msgid ""
"[WPI: from the :ref:`DEC` abbreviation CUSP, for ‘Commonly Used System "
"Program’, i.e., a utility program used by many people. Now rare.]"
msgstr ""
"[WPI: \\ :ref:`DEC`\\ の略語CUSP、‘Commonly Used System "
"Program’、すなわち多くの人に使われるユーティリティプログラムから。今やまれ。]"

#: ../../C/cuspy.rst:13
msgid "(of a program) Well-written."
msgstr "(プログラムについて) よく書かれた。"

#: ../../C/cuspy.rst:16
msgid ""
"Functionally excellent. A program that performs well and interfaces well to "
"users is cuspy. Oppose :ref:`rude`\\."
msgstr "機能的に優秀な。よく動き、ユーザーとうまくインターフェースするプログラムはcuspyです。\\ :ref:`rude`\\ と対立します。"

#: ../../C/cuspy.rst:21
msgid ""
"[NYU] Said of an attractive woman, especially one regarded as available. "
"Implies a certain curvaceousness."
msgstr "[NYU] 魅力的な女性、特に手の届きそうな女性について言われます。ある種の曲線美を含意します。"
